com.philips.cdp2.commlib.core.appliance

Class ApplianceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.philips.cdp2.commlib.core.appliance.ApplianceManager

  • public class ApplianceManager
extends Object
    The type ApplianceManager.

    Acts as a facade between an application and multiple DiscoveryStrategys. Any observer subscribed to an instance of this type is notified of events such as when an appliance is found or updated, or whenever an error occurs while performing discovery.

    The application should subscribe to notifications using the ApplianceManager.ApplianceListener interface. It's also possible to just obtain the set of available appliances using getAvailableAppliances()
